title: Rabid Ruth's Warning | American Horror Stories - Episode 3: "Drive In" (HD Clip)
author: AHS Crave
description: The third episode of American Horror Stories, titled "Drive In"— written by Manny Coto and directed by Eduardo Sánchez— stars Rhenzy Feliz (Chad), Madison Bailey (Kelley), Ben J. Pierce (Dee Dee), Naomi Grossman (Rabid Ruth), Leonardo Cecchi (Milo), Kyle Red Silverstein (Quinn), Amy Grabow (Tipper Gore), John Carroll Lynch (Larry Bitterman), Brandon Popo (Tillis), Courtney Hawkins (Ticket Taker), Stephanie Stanton (Reporter), Adrienne Barbeau (Verna), and Catherine Adell (Lanie).
